      • expectedOutput

        public String expectedOutput()
        Builds and returns a string representing to be used by clients to store the expected results text file. The format is: # Test test_num Expected Results test_description max_points results_to_be_assessed results_to_be_assessed ... The first line is simply used as a delimiter to make the expected results file slightly more readable.
